msgstr "通常会有守卫舰在此核查入境资格……但此刻，竟无一人阻拦你靠近联邦指挥部。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_emv_gilded.xml:14
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_emv_gilded.xml$//event[@name=\"EMV_GILDED_SECTOR_START\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
